{"tid":1720257,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"知唔知咩叫做fact check？","createTime":"2019-11-14T09:45:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T17:25:09.000Z","uid":97600,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"21685cafba61f6d877cc8b6e2976f12776dd056c","tid":1720257,"uid":97600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T09:45:50.000Z","msg":"我唔要見到啲標題寫住<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">未fact check</span></span>就發佈消息！！！<br />\n我唔要見到係tg cap出黎，然後得文字版敍述，連圖都冇張既capture！！！<br />\n<br />\n係呀，睇落好真呀，咁你有冇辦法出post前幫大家過濾下係咪真有其事呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一陣出咗post，咁啱你個「疑似」「未fc」post又上到熱門，好多人討論，好多正評，咁啱fake咗連登仔信以為真，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你能唔能夠承擔「發佈假消息」後帶黎既後果</span></span>？<br />\n<br />\n我明大家都好擔心手足受傷，好驚真係手足發生咁大件事，然後冇人討論。但係咁樣並唔能夠發揮討論區最大既功能，更嚴重既，係你<ins><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">有機會發佈緊假消息</span></strong></ins>！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記住！！！未證實既就唔好開post討論啦，除非有媒體已經撰文，咁仲叫可以出post講下。<br />\n<br />\n<ins>咁你到底想我點出post？</ins><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n例子：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zkZ7vdS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzkZ7vdS.png&h=0f2d8d45&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n呢張相睇落係咪好似有暴徒係香港搞事，而當刻又唔確定呢單野係咪由手足搞起，咁到底點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n只少你要知，幅圖入面係邊度，我地可以將幅圖拎去google，睇下有冇答案。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WuXMLRS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWuXMLRS.png&h=e91e10ed&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n跟住呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wHGE5Ss.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwHGE5Ss.png&h=4431aeeb&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n喔，原來on9協會都有post度出黎，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">即管禁埋入去，睇下係咪真係有件咁既事先！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n咁樣，你至少知道，幅圖最原本係喺邊度流傳出黎。如果係藍絲group既話，都唔好咁快斷定佢係假，記得禁入去睇下佢啲內容，再用你<ins><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">獨有</span></strong></ins>（藍絲冇架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）既<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">獨立思考／批判思考能力</span></strong>，幫大家諗下件事係咪真既。<br />\n<br />\n記住！！！用你既<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>好奇心</strong></span>click埋入去睇，分分鐘可以救全家！！！<br />\n<br />\n出post前諗一諗！！！幫我推上熱門俾啲人重溫下好冇呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（係因為樓主睇到未fc既情況好嚴重，最後討論完件事，件事都冇發生到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。重點係，明明我地可以將討論既時間做好其他救手足既工作架嘛！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）"},{"pid":"31cf1c8896d19b09aec91090a0016881e0cb6cb9","tid":1720257,"uid":97600,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T09:47:27.000Z","msg":"係呀，我用咗手足<strong><ins>原由柏実</ins></strong>個post啲圖，俾返個credit你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb08c2fb12df5f09168caf0c4b6a5660629f8608","tid":1720257,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T09:47:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0fbd49e55ae71d2a65c8a910dfbf2e7bc0d168e0","tid":1720257,"uid":97600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T09:50:26.000Z","msg":"幫樓主推上去好冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa6df954d5559afe5e53a173c6747ba7ef75df27","tid":1720257,"uid":312494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T09:56:04.000Z","msg":"p牌推吾到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf04cc0938408fb512a764268f08bd98ca6dd27f","tid":1720257,"uid":144522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-